.SH DESCRIPTION
The \f[B]dmdbctl\f[R] utility program performs create, read, update, or
delete operations on the observation database:
.TP
Create
Add nodes, sensors, and targets to the database.
.TP
Read
Read nodes, sensors, and targets from database.
Print the records to standard output.
.TP
Update
Update nodes, sensors, and targets in the database.
.TP
Delete
Delete nodes, sensors, and targets from the database.
.PP
Only nodes, sensors, and targets are supported.
All data attributes are passed through command\-line arguments.
